WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.426
Australia's financial landscape is changing. Lead AML is here to guide you through the transition to Tranche 2 compliance.

00:00:06.426 --> 00:00:14.054
The Anti-Money Laundering and Counter-Terrorism Financing laws are expanding, bringing new sectors under the regulatory umbrella.

00:00:14.054 --> 00:00:20.820
From real estate and legal services to accounting and precious metals—compliance is no longer optional. It's essential.

00:00:20.820 --> 00:00:28.186
Mark your calendars. By July 1st, 2026, these regulations will be fully operational across Australia.

00:00:28.186 --> 00:00:35.135
The goal is clear: to protect our economy from financial crime and ensure transparency in every transaction.

00:00:35.135 --> 00:00:42.188
Meeting these standards requires robust customer due diligence, ongoing monitoring, and precise reporting.

00:00:42.188 --> 00:00:48.431
Lead AML provides the expertise and tools you need to navigate these complexities with confidence and ease.

00:00:48.431 --> 00:00:54.753
Don't wait for the deadline. Start your compliance journey today to ensure a seamless transition for your business.

00:00:54.753 --> 00:00:57.753
Lead AML. Professional compliance for a safer future. Visit us at leadaml.com.au.
